The idea is really simple. It is just a two pointers solution where left advances only when a value is encountered for the first time, while right scans the whole array.
At the end, left index will point to the last unique element and I add 1 to obtain the length of the result (as per description we can ignore remaining portion of the array).

O(n-1) time complexity because I am starting the for cycle from the second element till the end.

